{"tid":690981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔准唔笑！】見外長木無表情？ 俄電視台P圖改到金仔有笑容","createTime":"2018-06-05T09:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T15:10:17.000Z","uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b289ca6eca31b295ba6304e2463f1cdbc1121d7a","tid":690981,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180605/large/1528183381_33ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180605%2Flarge%2F1528183381_33ae.jpg&h=f6f34369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前北韓領袖金正恩與到訪平壤的俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫（Sergei Lavrov）會面，其間拍照留念，不過俄羅斯國營電視疑不滿金正恩木無表情，竟涉嫌用電腦修圖將金正恩修改成面帶笑容。<br />\n<br />\n北韓領袖金正恩在下周與美國總統會面前，先於日前在平壤與俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫會面。消息指，雖然金正恩在席間有笑容，但金正恩和拉夫羅夫握手讓傳媒拍照時卻木無表情。<br />\n<br />\n不過，親普京的電視台「Russia 1」在節目《新聞一周》卻播出一張金正恩臉帶微笑握手的照片，惹來改圖疑雲，彭博通訊社莫斯科分局副局長羅斯（Scott Rose）在Twitter上揶揄：「俄國電視台以電腦修圖，為與拉夫羅夫會面的金正恩加上笑容。」<br />\n<br />\n其實俄羅斯外交部官方twitter賬戶也很誠實，發佈的相片及影片均見金正恩木無表情，看來這電視台是擦鞋出醜了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180605/58279041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F58279041&d=X3RJmpT%2FhfxEqYimeumNsv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a34d2471\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F58279041&h=c7f8a91f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180605/58279041</a>"},{"pid":"0df10d3d0303c230caa40aa06b2f660ae5977439","tid":690981,"uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141111/large/11ce2pnewt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141111%2Flarge%2F11ce2pnewt.jpg&h=280671ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起依張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa1d6b875eb0f1e576f7510586edd8124c21b55","tid":690981,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551913e7e74597a5a437a0dedda606ba4deeeaf2","tid":690981,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0df10d3d0303c230caa40aa06b2f660ae5977439","tid":690981,"uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141111/large/11ce2pnewt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141111%2Flarge%2F11ce2pnewt.jpg&h=280671ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起依張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"不如一槍打死我"},{"pid":"d0e01a874f31a0f4b9ce145a0f688e5578af7ab2","tid":690981,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"覆舟口"},{"pid":"670e3a16fe08612e8827d39c8f1807dd3f0507e6","tid":690981,"uid":53027,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/215518_b5b224c28a821cdb3e3a089bf4c5b4c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F215518_b5b224c28a821cdb3e3a089bf4c5b4c6.png&h=4e99ed12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f9443e43c0372957a47170a14632b6627550ba3","tid":690981,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"掌門人，super"},{"pid":"ce06c109ab3b928b4197d0d9bc2ee173ed7ec9dd","tid":690981,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"